Package it.polimi.ingsw.client.gui.controllers

Class MatchActiveController

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.client.gui.controllers.GUIController
it.polimi.ingsw.client.gui.controllers.MatchActiveController
public class MatchActiveController
extends GUIController
This is the main game controller. Manages 3D interaction and match evolution. For this purpose, we find here two different models. - One is graphical, and hides 3D from code. Can be driven into inconsistent states, with invalid moves in Hardcore mode, as the user is free to move. Every graphical rendered move originates in a change in this model and vice versa. - The second one is very lightweight, and it's updated only with approved changes server-side. In this way it's always up-to-date and consistent with the server-side one; and it's used to revert an inconsistent state of the graphical one.
